information: Empresa de Comercio y Turismo S.L, with CIF: B67103846, founded in 2017 and directed by Ms. Meroua Bouziane, is an importer, wholesaler and distributor of ethnic food products, with a qualitative positioning guided by the following values: RESPECT, SERIOUSNESS AND PASSION We import the best varieties of dates in the world, deglet nour, an Argentine variety from the Tolga Sahara, characterized by its unique drop, its great energy contribution and nutritional richness (antioxidants, vitamins). We offer a fresh and carefully selected date to have the best quality. In addition, we offer more than 300 articles, with a wide range of products under our own brands: Hamoud Boualem, Nounours, Mama, Ela, Nouara, El Sabah, Azahara
